Bootcamp Project 1

Objective

The objective of Day 4 was to create Gold business summary datasets, load reporting tables into Azure SQL Database, and finalize project documentation and GitHub submission.

Gold Data Flows Created
- df_gold_sales_summary
- df_gold_category_sales
- df_gold_top_products

Gold Business Outputs:
sales_summary_gold
- daily sales KPI summary.
category_sales_summary_gold
- Sales performance aggregated by category.
top_products_gold
- Top-performing products based on quantity and revenue.

Gold to SQL Reporting Pipeline
- Pipeline Created
 - pl_gold_to_sql_reporting
Copy Activities
- copy_sales_summary_to_sql
- copy_category_sales_to_sql
- copy_top_products_to_sql

SQL Reporting Validation
Validation queries were executed to confirm:
- successful data loading
- correct row counts
- reporting data accuracy
- Power BI Integration

Azure SQL reporting tables were connected to Power BI for dashboard creation and reporting.

Final Deliverables Uploaded
- Documentation
- SQL Scripts
- Screenshots
- ADF ARM Template / JSON
- Architecture Diagram
- README File

Key Learnings
- Gold layer business modeling
- Reporting table creation
- Gold to SQL ingestion
- Business KPI aggregation
- GitHub project documentation
